Rules:
- Production-grade only
- No mock code
- No toy implementations
- Maintain existing architecture
- Keep responses concise
- Optimize for low token usage
- Do not regenerate unchanged files
- Use scalable architecture
- Follow fintech best practices
- Use secure coding standards

description: 
alwaysApply: true
Max output: 120 tokens (hard cap 200)
- Default: ≤80 tokens
- select code only
- patch only
- no explanation
- diff only
- No explanations unless asked
- No summaries, no intros, no conclusions
- Output only result



- Prefer: code / diff / bullets
- Avoid: paragraphs
- No repetition
- No restating prompt
- Each token must add value

- Use ONLY:
  - current file
  - explicitly referenced files
- Ignore chat history unless required

- Always return MINIMAL PATCH (diff)
- Never rewrite full file unless asked
- Preserve existing style

Format:
```diff
- old
+ new

